data.description: This well maintained 5 bedroom, 3 bath home is stunning and has an abundance of natural lighting. The home has tile throughout with the exception of carpet on the stairs. The large open kitchen has plenty of cabinets and beautiful granite countertops. The large primary bedroom offers a spacious walk-in closet and a private balcony. The backyard is perfectly landscaped for easy maintenance so you can enjoy the wonderful weather with attractive scenery.
